{"tid":684731,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱同男朋友分咗手","createTime":"2018-05-30T19:21:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-17T09:26:01.000Z","uid":142854,"like":4,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"589517c8d768ad441ca02fb925dd9e4f07e840f7","tid":684731,"uid":142854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T19:21:34.000Z","msg":"同佢係中學識 好記得佢係中四陸運會之後同我表白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果時佢打波田徑讀書樣樣勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  而我只係一個廢人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我諗唔到點解佢會揀我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n望住佢同我既距離越黎越遠<br />\n由佢中學幫男拔拎到唔少學界冠軍 而我只係個唔做運動既懶人<br />\n去到而家佢做緊份50K既工 我只係做緊份25K既政府工<br />\n我個心真係好難受 好自卑<br />\n我諗唔到有咩可以俾到佢 除咗滿足佢性慾之外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢有話過會照顧我一世 但我上個禮拜都係同佢講分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n八年感情啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n對唔住啊 你將來會搵到一個更配得起你既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87a61975050727a491d4cd5d8cf259104d9b974c","tid":684731,"uid":35776,"like":22,"dislike":3,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"589517c8d768ad441ca02fb925dd9e4f07e840f7","tid":684731,"uid":142854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T19:21:34.000Z","msg":"同佢係中學識 好記得佢係中四陸運會之後同我表白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果時佢打波田徑讀書樣樣勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  而我只係一個廢人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我諗唔到點解佢會揀我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n望住佢同我既距離越黎越遠<br />\n由佢中